thread.title_full: 42nd Street Photo reviewed by Santiago Alvarez

author: Santiago Alvarez
title: Santiago Alvarez
text: This the first time I have purchased anything from 42nd street photo and I am very impressed by how fast and efficient the process was. Also very impressed that someone actually called to confirm information on the order. I would definitely come back.
